								class="material-icons right">arrow_drop_down</i></a></li>
				</ul>
				<ul class="side-nav" id="mobile-demo">
					<li><a href="/find">Find</a></li>
					<li><a href="/profile">Profile</a></li>
					<li><a href="#">Notifications<span class="new badge">0</span></a></li>
